'''Mac向苹果芯片迁移'''是[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]的一项为期两年的架构迁移计划。这一计划预期将[[麦金塔|Mac电脑]]从[[英特尔|英特尔]]的[[x86-64|x86-64]]的处理器平台迁移至[[ARM架构|ARM64]]架构的[[Apple_Silicon|Apple Silicon]]。苹果公司CEO[[蒂姆·库克|蒂姆·库克]]在2020年6月22日的[[苹果全球开发者大会|苹果全球开发者大会]](WWDC)宣布了这一计划。<ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22" />

这是苹果第三次将Mac迁移到新的[[指令集|指令集]]上。<ref name="CNET1">{{cite news|last1=Shankland|first1=Stephen|title=Apple gives Macs a brain transplant with new Arm chips starting this year|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-gives-macs-a-brain-transplant-with-new-arm-chips/|accessdate=June 23, 2020|work=[[CNet|CNet]]|date=June 22, 2020|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217001241/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-gives-macs-a-brain-transplant-with-new-arm-chips/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第一次是在1994年将Mac从摩托罗拉68000架构迁移至PowerPC平台，第二次是在2005年6月宣布的[[苹果向英特尔平台迁移|从PowerPC平台迁移至英特尔x86]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Honan|first1=Mathew|title=WWDC: Apple drops IBM PowerPC line for Intel chips|url=https://www.macworld.com/article/1045159/powerpcintel.html|accessdate=June 23, 2020|work=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|date=June 5, 2005|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126120023/https://www.macworld.com/article/1045159/powerpcintel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple to Use Intel Microprocessors Beginning in 2006|url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2005/06/06Apple-to-Use-Intel-Microprocessors-Beginning-in-2006/|accessdate=|author=|date=2005-06-06|format=|work=Apple Newsroom|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2018-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130185804/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2005/06/06Apple-to-Use-Intel-Microprocessors-Beginning-in-2006/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

苹果第一次使用ARM架构处理器是在1993年的[[Apple_Newton|Apple Newton]][[个人数码助理|个人数码助理]]中。在此之后，苹果大量地在其他如[[iPhone|iPhone]]、[[iPad|iPad]]、[[iPod|iPod]]和[[Apple_Watch|Apple Watch]]之类的产品中使用ARM架构。苹果从2009年透過收購[[P.A._Semi|P.A. Semi]]，开始自行研發ARM芯片。<ref name="Krazit, CNet 2009.09.18, re chip design" />

