==背景==

===苹果早期对ARM的使用===

在1990年，[[Apple_Newton|Apple Newton]]個人數位助理使得苹果成为了[[艾康电脑|艾康电脑]]生产的[[ARM架构|ARM架构]]处理器的第一个大客户。这个合作也促使了ARM项目被切割成为了一个单独的公司：[[安謀控股|安謀控股]]，苹果持股43%。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Smith |first1=Tony |title=Stylus counsel: The rise and fall of the Apple Newton MessagePad |url=https://www.theregister.com/Print/2013/09/17/20_years_of_the_apple_newton/ |website=The Register |publisher=The Register |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |ref=Advancing ARM |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034322/https://www.theregister.com/Print/2013/09/17/20_years_of_the_apple_newton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Kelion |first1=Leo |title=What is ARM and why is it worth £24bn? |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-36826095 |website=BBC News |publisher=BBC |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113073529/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-36826095 |dead-url=no }}</ref>ARM的全称也因此由“Acorn RISC Machine”（艾康精简指令集机器）变为了“Advanced RISC Machines”（高级精简指令集机器）。

===从PowerPC迁移至英特尔===
[[File:MacBook_Pro.png|thumb]]{{main|Mac向英特尔平台迁移}}

自从苹果在2005到2006年间进行的[[苹果向英特尔平台迁移|苹果向英特尔平台迁移]]计划后，所有新發表的Mac电脑均采用了英特尔的[[x86|x86]]架构[[中央处理器|处理器]]。[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]在2005年的[[苹果全球开发者大会|苹果全球开发者大会]]的演讲上表示英特尔处理器的能耗显著低于[[IBM|IBM]]的[[PowerPC|PowerPC]]，并称如果继续采用PowerPC的话，苹果将无法制造出其预期中的Mac来面对快速成长的市场对高性能工作站和高级筆記型電腦的需求：“在展望未来时，我们想制造许多令人惊叹的产品……但是我们不知道该如何用PowerPC来制造它们。”<ref name="McCracken, Fast Company 2020.06.24">{{cite news |last1=McCracken |first1=Harry |title=Apple’s 2005 and 2020 WWDC keynotes: Eerily similar—and worlds apart |url=https://www.fastcompany.com/90519918/apples-2005-and-2020-wwdc-keynotes-eerily-similar-and-worlds-apart |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |publisher=Fast Company |date=June 24, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109155206/https://www.fastcompany.com/90519918/apples-2005-and-2020-wwdc-keynotes-eerily-similar-and-worlds-apart |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title="Macintel" Q&A |url=https://everymac.com/mac-answers/macintel-faq/why-did-apple-switch-to-intel.html |publisher=EveryMac |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |date=January 16, 2006 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930190830/https://everymac.com/mac-answers/macintel-faq/why-did-apple-switch-to-intel.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2006年6月，苹果仅有高端桌上型电脑和伺服器還在使用PowerPC处理器。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Dalrymple |first1=Jim |title=One year later: How Apple's Intel transition is going |url=https://www.macworld.com/article/1051609/inteltransition.html |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[Macworld|Macworld]] |date=June 28, 2006 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126215916/https://www.macworld.com/article/1051609/inteltransition.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>硬件迁移结束的标志是2006年8月发布且在该年年底发货的基于英特尔处理器的[[Mac_Pro|Mac Pro]]和[[Xserve|Xserve]] <ref>{{cite web |title=Apple Introduces Xserve with Quad 64-bit Xeon Processors |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2006/08/07Apple-Introduces-Xserve-with-Quad-64-bit-Xeon-Processors/ |website=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=August 7, 2006 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034347/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2006/08/07Apple-Introduces-Xserve-with-Quad-64-bit-Xeon-Processors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Apple Unveils New Mac Pro Featuring Quad 64-bit Xeon Processors |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2006/08/07Apple-Unveils-New-Mac-Pro-Featuring-Quad-64-bit-Xeon-Processors/ |website=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=August 7, 2006 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115200242/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2006/08/07Apple-Unveils-New-Mac-Pro-Featuring-Quad-64-bit-Xeon-Processors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

苹果在硬件迁移结束后的第三年，也即2009年8月发布的[[Mac_OS_X_Snow_Leopard|Mac OS 10.6 "Snow Leopard"]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Mac OS X 10.6 Snow Leopard Installation and Setup Guide |url=https://manuals.info.apple.com/MANUALS/1000/MA1172/en_US/Snow_Leopard_Installation_Instructions.pdf |website=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=2009 |quote=To upgrade to Snow Leopard or install Snow Leopard for the first time, you must have a Mac with: An Intel processor |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127111822/https://manuals.info.apple.com/MANUALS/1000/MA1172/en_US/Snow_Leopard_Installation_Instructions.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>里结束了对PowerPC硬件的支持 <ref>{{cite web |title=Apple to Ship Mac OS X Snow Leopard on August 28 |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2009/08/24Apple-to-Ship-Mac-OS-X-Snow-Leopard-on-August-28/ |website=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=August 24, 2009 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209130359/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2009/08/24Apple-to-Ship-Mac-OS-X-Snow-Leopard-on-August-28/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而使用Rosetta翻译执行PowerPC程序的支持也在5年后的2011年7月发布的[[Mac_OS_X_Lion|Mac OS X 10.7 "Lion"]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Inside Mac OS X 10.7 Lion: Missing Front Row, Rosetta and Java runtime |url=https://appleinsider.com/articles/11/02/26/mac_os_x_lion_drops_front_row_java_runtime_rosetta.html |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[AppleInsider|AppleInsider]] |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127150940/https://appleinsider.com/articles/11/02/26/mac_os_x_lion_drops_front_row_java_runtime_rosetta.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Mac OS X Lion Available Today From the Mac App Store |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2011/07/20Mac-OS-X-Lion-Available-Today-From-the-Mac-App-Store/ |website=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=July 20, 2011 |archive-date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710135400/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2011/07/20Mac-OS-X-Lion-Available-Today-From-the-Mac-App-Store/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>中被放弃，宣告了整个迁移的结束。

===自研芯片的研发===
