[[File:Apple_A12Z.jpg|thumb]]處理器]]

2009年，苹果以2.78亿美元收购了半导体公司[[P.A._Semi|P.A. Semi]]<ref name="Krazit, CNet 2009.09.18, re acquisition">{{cite news |last1=Krazit |first1=Tom |title=Apple acquires low-power chip designer PA Semi |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-acquires-low-power-chip-designer-pa-semi/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[CNet|CNet]] |date=September 18, 2009 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034344/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-acquires-low-power-chip-designer-pa-semi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当时分析称苹果收购P.A. Semi是为了其所持知识产权和工程师人力资源<ref name="Krazit, CNet 2009.09.18, re engineers">{{cite news |last1=Krazit |first1=Tom |title=Report: Apple wants PA Semi's engineers, not its chips |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/report-apple-wants-pa-semis-engineers-not-its-chips/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[CNet|CNet]] |date=September 18, 2009 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034336/https://www.cnet.com/news/report-apple-wants-pa-semis-engineers-not-its-chips/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。苹果CEO[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]称P.A. Semi将会为iPod和iPhone研发[[SoC|SoC]]<ref name="Krazit, CNet 2009.09.18, re chip design">{{cite news |last1=Krazit |first1=Tom |title=Report: Apple's Jobs: PA Semi to design iPhone chips |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apples-jobs-pa-semi-to-design-iphone-chips/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[CNet|CNet]] |date=September 18, 2009 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034337/https://www.cnet.com/news/apples-jobs-pa-semi-to-design-iphone-chips/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此后，苹果发布了一系列配备自研处理器的产品。

自2011年起就有关于苹果将Mac迁移到自研ARM处理器的传闻。当时，SemiAccurate预测这一迁移将会发生在2013年年中 <ref name="SemiAccurate">{{cite web |last1=Demerjian |first1=Charlie |title=Apple dumps Intel from laptop lines |url=https://semiaccurate.com/2011/05/05/apple-dumps-intel-from-laptop-lines/ |website=SemiAccurate |publisher=Stone Arch Networking Services, Inc. |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |date=May 5, 2011 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128143547/https://semiaccurate.com/2011/05/05/apple-dumps-intel-from-laptop-lines/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，MacRumors称苹果正在测试一台拥有更大的妙控板的基于ARM的Mac <ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Testing ARM Based Mac Prototypes with Large Magic Trackpad?|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2014/05/25/arm-mac-magic-trackpad/|access-date=June 22, 2020|website=MacRumors|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203014634/https://www.macrumors.com/2014/05/25/arm-mac-magic-trackpad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，彭博社称苹果正在计划从2020年开始在Mac中使用其自研的ARM架构处理器 <ref>{{cite news |last1=King |first1=Ian |last2=Gurman |first2=Mark |title=Apple Plans to Use Its Own Chips in Macs From 2020, Replacing Intel |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-04-02/apple-is-said-to-plan-move-from-intel-to-own-mac-chips-from-2020 |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg]] |date=April 2, 2018 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128125747/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-04-02/apple-is-said-to-plan-move-from-intel-to-own-mac-chips-from-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

近年来，媒体报道中多次记载了苹果对英特尔研发速度和品质的疑惑和不满 <ref name="Hardwick, MacRumors 2020.06.25">{{cite news |last1=Hardwick |first1=Tim |title=Former Intel Engineer Claims Buggy Skylake Chips Hastened Apple's Switch to Custom Silicon |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2020/06/25/buggy-skylake-chips-hastened-apple-silicon/ |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |publisher=MacRumors |date=June 25, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219192854/https://www.macrumors.com/2020/06/25/buggy-skylake-chips-hastened-apple-silicon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。苹果在2017年的[[iPhone|iPhone]]中因为英特尔的[[调制解调器|基带芯片]]而遇到问题并导致预期生产时间节点的延误<ref>{{cite news |last1=Potuck |first1=Michael |title=Report: Apple’s custom 5G modems may not arrive until 2025 after ‘long and painful divorce’ with Intel |url=https://9to5mac.com/2019/05/15/apple-intel-divorce/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[9to5Mac|9to5Mac]] |date=May 15, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107224130/https://9to5mac.com/2019/05/15/apple-intel-divorce/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。与此同时，一份2018年的报告指出英特尔芯片的问题导致了苹果对MacBook的重新设计 <ref name="VentureBeat1">{{cite news |last1=Horwitz |first1=Jeremy |title=Apple reportedly redesigned basic MacBook after Intel chip issues |url=https://venturebeat.com/2018/08/17/apple-reportedly-redesigned-basic-macbook-after-intel-chip-issues/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] |date=August 17, 2018 |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131152824/https://venturebeat.com/2018/08/17/apple-reportedly-redesigned-basic-macbook-after-intel-chip-issues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年，苹果指责英特尔芯片库存的短缺导致了Mac销量的下降 <ref>{{cite news |last1=Allan |first1=Darren |title=Apple blames Intel’s processor shortage for slump in Mac sales |url=https://www.techradar.com/news/apple-blames-intels-processor-shortage-for-slump-in-mac-sales |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[TechRadar|TechRadar]] |date=May 3, 2019 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034322/https://www.techradar.com/news/apple-blames-intels-processor-shortage-for-slump-in-mac-sales |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

到2020年，有报道指出在2018款[[iPad_Pro|iPad Pro]]中使用的[[Apple_A12X_Bionic|Apple A12X Bionic]]处理器已经能够在性能上和在[[MacBook_Pro|MacBook Pro]]中使用的英特尔[[Core_i7|Core i7]]处理器打平 <ref name="VentureBeat2">{{cite news |last1=Horwitz |first1=Jeremy |title=Apple confirms Mac transition to ARM CPUs, Rosetta 2 Intel emulation |url=https://venturebeat.com/2020/06/22/apple-confirms-mac-transition-to-arm-cpus/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126235858/https://venturebeat.com/2020/06/22/apple-confirms-mac-transition-to-arm-cpus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2020年[[苹果全球开发者大会|苹果全球开发者大会]]前数月，多家媒体称苹果将会在此次活动中官方宣布迁移至自研芯片 <ref>{{cite web |last1=Gurman |first1=Mark |last2=Wu |first2=Debby |last3=King |first3=Ian |title=Apple Aims to Sell Macs With Its Own Chips Starting in 2021 |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-23/apple-aims-to-sell-macs-with-its-own-chips-starting-in-2021 |accessdate=June 21, 2020 |date=April 23, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903194931/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-23/apple-aims-to-sell-macs-with-its-own-chips-starting-in-2021 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Haselton |first1=Todd |title=Apple will stop using Intel chips in all Macs by 2021, top analyst says |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/06/22/new-macbook-pro-and-imac-coming-with-arm-chips-instead-of-intel---kuo.html |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127213415/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/06/22/new-macbook-pro-and-imac-coming-with-arm-chips-instead-of-intel---kuo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==迁移至苹果芯片==

苹果在2020年6月的苹果全球开发者大会中的一系列讲座中宣布了其将Mac迁移至苹果芯片的计划 <ref>{{cite news |last1=Warren |first1=Tom |title=Apple announces it will switch to its own processors for future Macs |url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/6/22/21295475/apple-mac-processors-arm-silicon-chips-wwdc-2020 |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622192505/https://www.theverge.com/2020/6/22/21295475/apple-mac-processors-arm-silicon-chips-wwdc-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整个迁移将持续“大约两年”，且第一台基于ARM的Mac将会在2020年年底前发布<ref name="ArsTechnica1"/><ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22" /> 类似的话在[[苹果向英特尔平台迁移|2005年到2006年苹果向英特尔平台迁移]]的过程中出现过，但那次迁移仅花了一年半 <ref name="VentureBeat2"/>。

所有[[macOS_Big_Sur|macOS Big Sur]]中的自带应用均将同时支持x86-64与ARM架构。其他应用（包括知名的[[Adobe_Photoshop|Adobe Photoshop]]、[[Final_Cut_Pro|Final Cut Pro]]和[[Microsoft_Word|Microsoft Word]]）则将类似地支持两个平台 <ref name="ArsTechnica1">{{cite news |last1=Axon |first1=Samuel |last2=Amadeo |first2=Ron |title=This is Apple’s roadmap for moving the first Macs away from Intel |url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/this-is-apples-roadmap-for-moving-the-first-macs-away-from-intel/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[ArsTechnica|ArsTechnica]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623082629/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/this-is-apples-roadmap-for-moving-the-first-macs-away-from-intel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

为了使x86原生应用也可以在基于ARM的Mac上运行，苹果将{{link-en|Rosetta 2|Rosetta 2|Rosetta 2}}这一[[二进制翻译|动态二进制翻译]]软件无缝嵌入了macOS Big Sur使得用户可以在无感知的情况下执行x86原生应用 <ref name="VentureBeat2"/><ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22" />。而[[通用二进制2|通用二进制2]]则可以令开发者同时支持[[x86-64|x86-64]]和[[ARM架构|ARM64]] <ref>{{Cite web|last=Axon|first=Samuel|date=June 22, 2020|title=This is Apple’s roadmap for moving the first Macs away from Intel|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/this-is-apples-roadmap-for-moving-the-first-macs-away-from-intel/|access-date=June 23, 2020|website=Ars Technica|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623082629/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/this-is-apples-roadmap-for-moving-the-first-macs-away-from-intel/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22" />。

为了方便为ARM架构的Mac开发软件，苹果向开发者借出一台基于ARM的原型Mac——[[Developer_Transition_Kit|Developer Transition Kit]]来做测试。这一原型Mac采用了经过大规模修改的[[iPad_Pro|iPad Pro]]硬件，并且被安放在了一个[[Mac_mini|Mac mini]]的外盒中 <ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22" /><ref name="VentureBeat2"/>。

前英特尔的主任工程师François Piednoël公开发表个人观点称英特尔近三年来在[[Skylake微架构|Skylake架构处理器]]中“异常糟糕”的品控导致苹果成为了“报告Skylake问题最多的组织”，这也成为了苹果从英特尔平台迁移走的導火線之一。英特尔的首席技术官Mike Mayberry则反驳称这种品控问题在任何CPU厂商中都可能大规模出现 <ref name="abnormally bad">{{cite news | work=PC Gamer | title=Intel insider claims it finally lost Apple because Skylake QA 'was abnormally bad' | first=Dave | last=James | date=June 24, 2020 | url=https://www.pcgamer.com/intel-skylake-why-apple-left/ | accessdate=August 6, 2020 | archive-date=2021-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131215404/https://www.pcgamer.com/intel-skylake-why-apple-left/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===性能===

在宣布迁移后不久的一次采访中，苹果的软件工程高級副總裁[[克雷格·费德里吉|克雷格·费德里吉]]（{{lang|en|Craig Federighi}}）高度赞扬了[[Developer_Transition_Kit|Developer Transition Kit]]（DTK）这一原型机的性能，称：“即使是对于DTK这样一台用着我们永远都不会放到Mac里的芯片的机器，一台仅仅是为了迁移而存在的机器，macOS都能在其上顺畅地运行。虽然这台机器根本不能作为评判未来的Mac的标准……但是你可以从中明白我们的芯片团队在根本没有努力的情况下能做到什么样子。而在未来的Mac的设计里他们会将会努力。”<ref name="Gruber, Daring Fireball 2020.06.24">{{cite news |last1=Gruber |first1=John |title=The Talk Show Remote from WWDC 2020, With Craig Federighi and Greg Joswiak |url=http://www.daringfireball.net/2020/06/the_talk_show_wwdc_2020 |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |publisher=Daring Fireball |date=June 24, 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101083443/https://daringfireball.net/2020/06/the_talk_show_wwdc_2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Long, The Startup, 2020.06.25">{{cite news |last1=Long |first1=Michael |title=Just How Fast Is Apple Silicon? |url=https://medium.com/swlh/just-how-fast-is-apple-silicon-a6d3e1804ba6 |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |publisher=The Startup |date=June 25, 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106120755/https://medium.com/swlh/just-how-fast-is-apple-silicon-a6d3e1804ba6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==影响==
===苹果公司===
这次迁移将会使得苹果公司得以降低成本，因为它不再需要购买其他公司生产的昂贵的CPU <ref name="CNET1"/>。

===英特尔===
有消息指出这将在短期内对英特尔带来中等程度的负面影响，理由是苹果占据英特尔年收入的2%到4% <ref name="Engadget2">{{cite news |last1=Holt |first1=Kris |title=Apple ditches Intel for its own processors in Macs |url=https://www.engadget.com/apple-silicon-arm-mac-processor-intel-182826202.html |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208170031/https://www.engadget.com/apple-silicon-arm-mac-processor-intel-182826202.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>且其Mac电脑在全球市场仅占7% <ref name="2019 PC">{{cite news |url=https://www.gartner.com/en/newsroom/press-releases/2020-01-13-gartner-says-worldwide-pc-shipments-grew-2-point-3-percent-in-4q19-and-point-6-percent-for-the-year |title=Gartner Says Worldwide PC Shipments Grew 2.3% in 4Q19 and 0.6% for the Year |publisher=[[Gartner|Gartner]] |date=January 13, 2020 |accessdate=February 3, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224043234/https://www.gartner.com/en/newsroom/press-releases/2020-01-13-gartner-says-worldwide-pc-shipments-grew-2-point-3-percent-in-4q19-and-point-6-percent-for-the-year |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在长期上，有猜测认为这次迁移将使得其他PC制造商重新考虑其对英特尔[[x86|x86]]架构的依赖，因为Mac经常在個人電腦行業裡帶領轉變<ref name="Bloomberg1"/><ref name="Jean-Louis Gassée, 2020.06.21">{{cite news |last1=Gassée |first1=Jean-Louis |title=ARM Mac Impact On Intel |url=https://mondaynote.com/arm-mac-impact-on-intel-9641a8e73dca |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |publisher=Monday Note |date=June 21, 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622054518/https://mondaynote.com/arm-mac-impact-on-intel-9641a8e73dca |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===AMD===
由于这次迁移也同时标志着苹果放弃AMD和英伟达等第三方显卡，这也会对AMD造成短期负面影响。

===开发者===
因为[[iOS|iOS]]平台的应用将可以在ARM架构的Mac上运行，苹果希望就此整合其软件和硬件使得开发者开发的应用能够在整个苹果平台上运行 <ref name="Engadget1"/>。

===用户===
由于苹果芯片相较于英特尔处理器功耗更低，这次迁移可能带来更纤薄轻巧的Mac笔记本 <ref name="Bloomberg1">{{cite news |last1=Gurman |first1=Mark |title=In a first, Apple plans to shift to its own processors to power new Mac computers |url=https://fortune.com/2020/06/09/in-a-first-apple-plans-to-shift-to-its-own-processors-to-power-new-mac-computers/ |accessdate=June 22, 2020 |work=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]] |agency=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg]] |date=June 9, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207034336/https://fortune.com/2020/06/09/in-a-first-apple-plans-to-shift-to-its-own-processors-to-power-new-mac-computers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[iOS|iOS]]平台上的应用将可以在ARM架构的Mac上运行，这使得Mac平台的软件变得更加丰富 <ref name="Engadget1">{{cite news |last1=Lee |first1=Nicole |title=iOS apps will run natively on ARM-powered Macs |url=https://www.engadget.com/ios-apps-arm-powered-macs-192046502.html |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208172634/https://www.engadget.com/ios-apps-arm-powered-macs-192046502.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而迁移到苹果专有的芯片上将会显著打击甚至完全阻止在普通PC硬件上运行macOS的行为（这一行为违背macOS的软件协议，即俗称的[[Hackintosh|Hackintosh]]“黑苹果”玩家行为） <ref name="Gewirtz, ZDNet 2020.06.24">{{cite news |last1=Gewirtz |first1=David |title=Will Apple Silicon kill the Hackintosh? The odds against a self-built MacOS Arm computer |url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/will-apple-silicon-kill-the-hackintosh/ |accessdate=June 24, 2020 |publisher=ZDNet |date=June 24, 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115131543/https://www.zdnet.com/article/will-apple-silicon-kill-the-hackintosh/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Fagioli, BetaNews 2020.06.22">{{cite news |last1=Fagioli |first1=Brian |title=Macs will use ARM-based Apple processors instead of Intel — is Hackintosh dead? |url=https://betanews.com/2020/06/22/apple-macos-intel-arm/ |accessdate=June 24, 2020 |publisher=BetaNews |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117172832/https://betanews.com/2020/06/22/apple-macos-intel-arm/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

苹果用于在[[英特尔|英特尔]]平台的Mac上启动[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]的[[引导程序|双启动引导软件]][[启动转换|启动转换]]也将不会出现在基于苹果芯片的Mac上。2020年6月，苹果声称其无意在基于苹果芯片的Mac上“支持直接启动到Windows”。苹果的高级软件工程副总裁[[克雷格·费德里吉|克雷格·费德里吉]]称[[虚拟化|虚拟化]]是一个替代方案：“完全虚拟化将会是一条出路……虚拟化软件效率可以很高，因此无法直接启动到Windows其实不是什么大问题。”<ref name="Warren, TheVerge 2020.06.24" >{{Cite web|last=Warren|first=Tom|date=June 24, 2020|title=Apple’s new ARM-based Macs won’t support Windows through Boot Camp|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/6/24/21302213/apple-silicon-mac-arm-windows-support-boot-camp|access-date=June 28, 2020|website=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207065245/https://www.theverge.com/2020/6/24/21302213/apple-silicon-mac-arm-windows-support-boot-camp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Axon, ArsTechnica 2020.06.24">{{Cite web|last=Axon|first=Samuel|date=June 24, 2020|title=Here’s what’s happening to Boot Camp amid the Apple silicon transition|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/heres-whats-happening-to-boot-camp-amid-the-apple-silicon-transition/|access-date=June 28, 2020|website=Ars Technica|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116195255/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/06/heres-whats-happening-to-boot-camp-amid-the-apple-silicon-transition/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 微软没有评价是否会针对基于ARM的Windows提供除[[OEM|OEM]]预装以外的授权 <ref name="Warren, TheVerge 2020.06.24" />。而依靠微软的 Windows for Arm 项目，不少个人电脑玩家已经成功将 Windows 虚拟化到 Arm 架构的 M1 MacBook 上運行，通过 Windows for Arm 的中介实现了 Windows x86 架构软件的运行。<ref>{{cite news |first1=Aimo |last1=IT 之家|title=苹果 M1 Mac 性能爆表缺软件，可 MacBook 真的不能装 Win10 吗 |url=https://www.ithome.com/0/522/885.htm |accessdate=Feb 28, 2021 |publisher=IT 之家 |date=Dec 24, 2020 }}</ref>

==评价==
作为如同2005年[[苹果向英特尔平台迁移|苹果向英特尔平台迁移]]的迁移项目，本次迁移在受到褒奖的同时也被质疑会觸發消費者延遲或取消購買蘋果電腦產品（英文裡稱為「{{link-en|歐思邦效應|Osborne effect}}」）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Gassée |first1=Jean-Louis |title=Osborning The Mac. Or Not. |url=https://mondaynote.com/osborning-the-mac-or-not-f0bbf4c319f0 |website=Monday Note |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |date=June 14, 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614220541/https://mondaynote.com/osborning-the-mac-or-not-f0bbf4c319f0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC1">{{cite news |last1=Kelion |first1=Leo |title=Apple Mac computers make jump to its own chips |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-53142989 |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128192957/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-53142989 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Stern, WSJ 2020.06.25">{{cite news |last1=Stern |first1=Joanna |title=The Apple Devices You Should — and Should NOT — Buy Right Now |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-apple-devices-you-shouldand-should-notbuy-right-now-11593096901 |accessdate=June 25, 2020 |publisher=The Wall Street Journal |date=June 25, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131023107/https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-apple-devices-you-shouldand-should-notbuy-right-now-11593096901 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Wired表达了对苹果设计师能否把一个手机处理器的性能提升到[[Mac_Pro|Mac Pro]]级别的质疑，并且质疑苹果含混不清地说会在ARM架构的Mac上支持英特尔x86原生应用“很多年”到底是多久。<ref name="Wired1">{{cite news |last1=Barrett |first1=Brian |title=Apple's Intel Breakup Will Reshape Macs—and Beyond |url=https://www.wired.com/story/apple-will-put-its-own-chips-into-macs/ |accessdate=June 23, 2020 |work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] |date=June 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118052138/https://www.wired.com/story/apple-will-put-its-own-chips-into-macs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Apple PR 2020.06.22">{{Cite web|title=Apple announces Mac transition to Apple silicon|url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2020/06/apple-announces-mac-transition-to-apple-silicon/|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-06-22|format=|work=Apple Newsroom|publisher=|archive-date=2020-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622185215/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2020/06/apple-announces-mac-transition-to-apple-silicon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而在正面评价中，Lauren Giret赞扬了苹果可能因为其软硬件的紧密结合和大量能在新平台运行的软件而“在微软失败的领域取得成功” <ref>{{Cite web|date=June 23, 2020|title=Opinion: Apple seems poised to succeed where Microsoft failed with Windows 10 on ARM|url=https://www.onmsft.com/editorial/opinion-apple-seems-poised-to-succeed-where-microsoft-failed-with-windows-10-on-arm|access-date=June 30, 2020|website=OnMSFT.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127061752/https://www.onmsft.com/editorial/opinion-apple-seems-poised-to-succeed-where-microsoft-failed-with-windows-10-on-arm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

